-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/39031532_736791201851287_4149678069899420458_n.png?_nc_cat=101&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=9Rd790zlIn4Q7kNvgH6K2xu&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYBHJR66Zns5DdqWma1_7G7rvQATZ6OQnT2F2X1nFGdcuQ&oe=6739BDC6"}, "display_name": "EscapeVR: The Basement", "keywords": [], "long_description": "EscapeVR: The Basement is an 'Escape The Room' genre game which was inspired by real-life escape games and written from the ground up as a room-scale virtual reality experience.\n\nExplore the environment, solve puzzles, discover useful items, investigate clues, and find your way through a total of seven rooms in three areas to -hopefully- escape the basement!\n\n- Solve over a dozen puzzles, which includes smaller ones like finding keys or codes up to large ones which involve complex interactions with daunting machinery.\n\n- Explore three distinct areas with seven rooms, a total of 130 square meters, and more than 200 items to interact with. The game is designed for room scale and features a teleporting system.\n\n- In case you get stuck, a built-in hint system provides you with clues. You\u2019ll also get in-game statistics about your performance, and there are achievements to unlock!\n\nWill you take on the challenge? Will you manage to escape the basement?", "short_description": "You find yourself locked in the cell of an unknown basement with nothing else than a bed and a toilet. Can you escape? Explore the environment, solve puzzles, investigate clues, and find your way through a total of 7 rooms to -hopefully- escape the basement of this VR escape room game."}]}, "developer_name": null, "developer_privacy_policy_url": "https://www.escapevr.net/privacy-policy", "developer_terms_of_service_url": null, "publisher_name": "Five Mind Creations UG (haftungsbeschr\u00e4nkt)", "support_website_url": null, "website_url": "https://www.escapevr.net/", "category": null, "comfort_rating": null, "comfort_tags": [], "context_category": {"